1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:07,780
So, myself and my husband were out one evening a couple of years ago, sat in the car chatting down by the water parked outside a pub.

2
00:00:08,600 --> 00:00:13,100
My husband is one of these people who likes to help all animals or insects that he can.

3
00:00:13,980 --> 00:00:16,560
So you can imagine how this story may turn out.

4
00:00:17,380 --> 00:00:23,220
We heard a thud, so we got out of the car and a pheasant had flown into the wall of the pub and landed on the floor.

5
00:00:23,940 --> 00:00:27,260
So my husband immediately went up to it to see how it was.

6
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,780
This is not an area where you would normally see a pheasant.

7
00:00:31,420 --> 00:00:35,040
The pheasant was fine, was just a bit dazed and in shock.

8
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:41,980
So, my husband decided we should try and take it to a more pheasant appropriate place in the car.

9
00:00:42,840 --> 00:00:45,260
This would be around a 15 minute drive.

10
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:48,240
So I agreed as I felt sorry for it.

11
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:54,820
The plan was, my husband was to wrap the pheasant up in his jacket and I was to have the pheasant on my lap.

12
00:00:55,460 --> 00:00:56,440
So we did.

13
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:02,980
Well, we got about 10 minutes up the road and the pheasant was still in shock and sat still on my lap.

14
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:08,080
My husband decides it's cold and without warning, puts on the fan in the car.

15
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,200
The pheasant shit itself.

16
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:15,880
It was flying around the car, I was screaming and my husband was still trying to drive.

17
00:01:16,740 --> 00:01:18,440
It was flapping all over the car.

18
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,220
Pooping as it went.

19
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:26,580
My husband pulled over to the nearest area with grass and trees and we opened the car door to get the pheasant out.

20
00:01:27,260 --> 00:01:29,360
Well that was another 20 minute job.

21
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:30,580
I know.

22
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:33,560
I cannot believe this story is true either.

23
00:01:34,420 --> 00:01:37,640
But believe me, it is not an experience I want again.

